{"title":"大节日，长江上","authors":["徐迟"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":10,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"大节日，长江上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐迟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我国地图这一点上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江流过的这个地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右岸黄鹄矶头黄鹤楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左岸晴川阁、鹦鹉洲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少的历史记载，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少的著名战役。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来这里饮酒赋诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少英雄豪杰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个伟大的心灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天也来到了这里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俯视大江奔流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝望移动的风篷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼底是三鼎足的武汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静静的龟山蛇山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贯穿南北的铁路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他问：“黄鹤知何去？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他那时正十分年轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在探索真理的声音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时是1918年曙光初透，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉睡的民族开始在觉醒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他站在苍茫的烟雨下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思索祖国的出路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在沉沉的黑暗中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他讯问祖国的前途。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“把酒酹滔滔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心潮逐浪高，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东这样歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摆渡过了长江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渡江北上后，他听到了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月革命的炮声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马克思列宁的智慧之火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点亮了中国革命的火把。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火把点亮在井冈山上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征道上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陕北延河之傍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而光耀照遍了全国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"武装的人民战斗了三十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建立起新型的共和国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这欢声雷动的大节日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江上显出壮观的景色。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江流过的这个地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黄鹤楼晴川阁之中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龟山蛇山之上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一条宝带横空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄伟而美丽的宝带，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平和友谊的化身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五年计划的凯旋门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义的里程碑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义的七色长虹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一座理想的桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过长江去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使这天堑变通途。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梨子的土地和荔枝的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连成一片，通行无阻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从柏林，到河内，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众兄弟拉起了友谊的手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，高贵的桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大理石和钢铁的桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先进技术的桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"武汉长江大桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自从共产党启宏图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥就被孕育在蓝图上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"模型上显出桥的外形，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工地上开来了建设大军。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（那是我的幸福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看到了这座桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在水下、水面、水上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天天生长，形成。）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！我们现在还能感到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一开动之后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸为之山崩地裂的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震动打桩机的威力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！我们现在还能听到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那大型钻机的十字钻头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉重地锤击江底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩盘的“啃！啃！啃！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！我们现在还能看到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那桥梁工地上的美景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入夜灯火辉煌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比银河掉落到人间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我曾走下围堰去直到江底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比走到了海龙王的龙宫里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也曾攀登到最高的钢梁顶上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算真到了云霄里把武汉眺望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道我们是有力量的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却不知道我们力量这样大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道我们有美妙的未来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知道如今已经这般美妙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大节日，长江上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢声雷动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大工程大功告成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，长桥、车水、马龙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞驰过长江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只消一分钟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江涛、车声、汽笛、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片歌唱声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的理想，歌唱在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大节日，长江上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我们的心又飞去了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞翔在西陵峡南津关。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}